None
00:00:15,512 --> 00:00:18,679
What do you mean Freya's the reason
why Ci-N is in Section E?

None
00:00:18,681 --> 00:00:19,515
Ci-N kissed me.

None
00:00:19,516 --> 00:00:21,307
And Freya got mad because…

None
00:00:21,309 --> 00:00:22,643
apparently, she likes Ci-N too.

None
00:00:22,643 --> 00:00:25,394
So, we got into a fight and
she made stories about Ci-N.

None
00:00:25,396 --> 00:00:28,231
After that, everyone accused
Ci-N of being a thief.

None
00:00:28,233 --> 00:00:30,609
Ci-N, a thief? He's too childish for that.

None
00:00:30,609 --> 00:00:31,443
Hey, he's not childish.

None
00:00:31,443 --> 00:00:32,195
You want pancakes?

None
00:00:32,362 --> 00:00:36,155
You offered, but it's not cooked.
You're really something else, kid.

None
00:00:36,156 --> 00:00:37,240
Then just cook it.

None
00:00:37,241 --> 00:00:38,033
Is that him?

None
00:00:38,034 --> 00:00:39,451
He stole it!

None
00:00:39,451 --> 00:00:40,993
Are you sure? You have proof?

None
00:00:40,994 --> 00:00:42,329
Don't butt in!

None
00:00:42,329 --> 00:00:44,164
What if I punch you in the mouth?!

None
00:00:44,164 --> 00:00:46,457
- I will really do it!
- Jay-jay, just let them be!

None
00:00:46,459 --> 00:00:47,417
Oh my…

None
00:00:47,418 --> 00:00:49,712
Ci-N. You did it again?

None
00:00:50,213 --> 00:00:51,505
Why didn't you tell me?!

None
00:00:51,506 --> 00:00:53,590
I'm scared you'll look at me differently.

None
00:00:53,591 --> 00:00:56,551
It's as if you're proving
that what they're saying is true!

None
00:00:56,552 --> 00:00:57,594
Jay-jay!

None
00:00:57,887 --> 00:00:59,054
Why did you do that?

None
00:00:59,389 --> 00:01:01,847
I miss my friends from Section E.

None
00:01:01,848 --> 00:01:03,183
And Ci-N is one of them.

None
00:01:03,518 --> 00:01:05,102
That's the money you paid that bitch!

None
00:01:05,102 --> 00:01:06,727
Ci-N didn't steal that!

None
00:01:06,728 --> 00:01:07,728
I did!

None
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:11,066
I'll pay for the cafe's entire
earnings for the day.

None
00:01:11,066 --> 00:01:13,025
Just get rid of all the customers here.

None
00:01:13,027 --> 00:01:14,778
Most especially the judgmental ones.

None
00:01:17,656 --> 00:01:18,740
Here it comes.

None
00:01:19,492 --> 00:01:20,993
Excuse me, Ma'am, Sir.

None
00:01:21,286 --> 00:01:22,328
Here's your order.

None
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:26,540
Coffee.

None
00:01:27,834 --> 00:01:28,918
Iced tea.

None
00:01:30,210 --> 00:01:31,462
Enjoy your meal.

None
00:01:31,962 --> 00:01:33,131
Thank you.

None
00:01:37,885 --> 00:01:39,387
Here. Eat up.

None
00:01:40,138 --> 00:01:42,180
About time.
I'm so famished.

None
00:01:42,347 --> 00:01:43,849
I've been biking a long way.

None
00:01:53,692 --> 00:01:56,862
I'm drenched in sweat.
I'm so hungry.

None
00:01:58,364 --> 00:01:59,281
Mmmm.

None
00:01:59,283 --> 00:02:00,450
It's so tasty!

None
00:02:02,826 --> 00:02:03,826
Why?

None
00:02:04,162 --> 00:02:04,787
Hmm?

None
00:02:04,787 --> 00:02:06,496
Why did you do that for Ci-N?

None
00:02:11,669 --> 00:02:13,253
Ci-N is like a brother to me.

None
00:02:14,546 --> 00:02:15,882
You know that feeling when...

None
00:02:16,299 --> 00:02:19,050
an older sister can't bear
to see her brother get hurt?

None
00:02:19,051 --> 00:02:20,218
That's how it felt.

None
00:02:21,804 --> 00:02:23,097
Don't you have any siblings?

None
00:02:23,806 --> 00:02:25,681
Why do you care so much for Ci-N?

None
00:02:25,682 --> 00:02:27,852
I wasn't informed this is
gonna be an interview.

None
00:02:28,019 --> 00:02:29,145
I'm just curious.

None
00:02:32,981 --> 00:02:34,691
My Auntie told me
I had an older brother.

None
00:02:34,692 --> 00:02:37,361
But my mom put him up for adoption.

None
00:02:37,611 --> 00:02:38,820
I never met him.

None
00:02:46,704 --> 00:02:49,164
What's up? Have you told Jay yet?

None
00:03:18,318 --> 00:03:20,195
How about you?
Don't you have any siblings?

None
00:03:20,405 --> 00:03:23,032
I do. She's in Japan.
With my parents.

None
00:03:23,241 --> 00:03:24,908
She's eight years younger than me.

None
00:03:29,205 --> 00:03:30,538
Edrix, where are you?

None
00:03:30,539 --> 00:03:34,335
We just finished playing basketball.
We're starving. Let's go eat!

None
00:03:34,711 --> 00:03:35,794
I'll be there.

None
00:03:40,216 --> 00:03:41,258
[Yuri laughs]

None
00:03:42,217 --> 00:03:43,468
It's delicious.

None
00:03:49,641 --> 00:03:50,641
This is so good!

None
00:03:54,813 --> 00:03:58,025
I shouldn't be feeling this way.
I'm confused...

None
00:03:58,735 --> 00:04:01,570
All this time, I thought I loved Ella.

None
00:04:06,387 --> 00:04:09,218
But fuck. I will no longer deny it.

None
00:04:14,336 --> 00:04:16,713
I'm starting to feel something for Jay-jay.

None
00:04:19,172 --> 00:04:20,172
Delicious!

None
00:04:20,173 --> 00:04:21,466
I've finished it.

None
00:04:22,382 --> 00:04:25,136
But why her of all people?

None
00:04:26,512 --> 00:04:28,889
Why did I fall for the person Keifer hates?

None
00:04:31,559 --> 00:04:33,685
I'm the only one eating.
You might say I'm a glutton.

None
00:04:35,437 --> 00:04:36,605
Here's some more.

None
00:04:38,024 --> 00:04:39,192
Don't you want some?

None
00:04:46,072 --> 00:04:48,115
Keifer's just gonna use her.

None
00:04:48,117 --> 00:04:51,995
I don't know how, but I don't want
to see it nor imagine it.

None
00:04:53,915 --> 00:04:56,709
I don't think I can bear
seeing Jay-jay in tears.

None
00:05:02,464 --> 00:05:06,343
This tastes similar to the muffins
Auntie Gemma makes.

None
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:10,930
Have you ever had a boyfriend?

None
00:05:10,932 --> 00:05:11,932
Huh?!

None
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:14,142
Why the sudden question?

None
00:05:14,266 --> 00:05:15,641
I'm just asking.

None
00:05:17,855 --> 00:05:18,855
I have.

None
00:05:19,064 --> 00:05:20,065
Really?

None
00:05:20,733 --> 00:05:22,360
Why do you sound so surprised?

None
00:05:22,819 --> 00:05:25,278
As if I'm too ugly
to have a relationship.

None
00:05:25,529 --> 00:05:26,612
It's not that. What I mean is...

None
00:05:26,613 --> 00:05:28,303
But it's true. I had two.

None
00:05:29,658 --> 00:05:31,536
What happened?
Why did you break up?

None
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:35,288
The first one...

None
00:05:35,997 --> 00:05:38,250
he came out. Apparently,
he's actually gay.

None
00:05:38,375 --> 00:05:39,459
The second one...

None
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:42,547
he's in the hospital.

None
00:05:42,797 --> 00:05:43,839
Comatose.

None
00:05:44,841 --> 00:05:46,259
Why? What happened?

None
00:05:48,552 --> 00:05:49,928
I don't remember anymore.

None
00:05:50,221 --> 00:05:51,973
Anyway. Let's not talk about it.

None
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:54,559
How about you?
Share something about your love life.

None
00:05:54,809 --> 00:05:55,851
Oh, me?

None
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:57,519
Nothing serious.

None
00:05:57,894 --> 00:05:59,480
But I fell in love once.

None
00:06:00,189 --> 00:06:01,858
And she didn't love me back.

None
00:06:02,233 --> 00:06:03,233
Was it Ella?

None
00:06:03,985 --> 00:06:04,901
Oh...

None
00:06:04,901 --> 00:06:05,901
sorry.

None
00:06:07,362 --> 00:06:09,154
That's okay. It's all in the past.

None
00:06:09,156 --> 00:06:11,031
Really? Is that so?

None
00:06:11,033 --> 00:06:12,076
You're annoying.

None
00:06:12,367 --> 00:06:13,619
There's Ella!

None
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,788
[Jay-jay chuckles]

None
00:06:17,038 --> 00:06:18,206
You're so annoying, Jay.

None
00:06:20,041 --> 00:06:21,252
Eat something too.

None
00:06:21,961 --> 00:06:23,920
Go on. I don't really eat those.

None
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,255
Then why did you order them?

None
00:06:25,755 --> 00:06:26,798
No idea.

None
00:06:28,259 --> 00:06:29,427
You're really out of it!

None
00:06:33,973 --> 00:06:35,641
How will you go home later?

None
00:06:37,142 --> 00:06:39,685
I'll ride my bike.
It's too tiring, honestly.

None
00:06:39,687 --> 00:06:41,521
It's too far away.
I got drenched in sweat.

None
00:06:41,521 --> 00:06:42,521
Shall I take you home?

None
00:06:42,939 --> 00:06:43,939
Mmm?

None
00:08:14,781 --> 00:08:15,781
Keif.

None
00:08:18,076 --> 00:08:18,786
Hey.

None
00:08:19,036 --> 00:08:20,036
Damn.

None
00:08:20,829 --> 00:08:21,788
What's his problem?

None
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:23,374
You're in a bad mood, Keif?

None
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:24,916
That's why I followed.

None
00:08:25,125 --> 00:08:26,668
It's the Jay-jay situation.

None
00:08:27,622 --> 00:08:28,622
It's a mess.

None
00:08:29,379 --> 00:08:30,423
So...

None
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,880
what's the plan?

None
00:08:32,549 --> 00:08:35,635
Hopefully, Edrix can hack the CCTV records.

None
00:08:35,802 --> 00:08:37,929
Find proof that Ci-N didn't steal anything.

None
00:08:38,889 --> 00:08:40,390
Almost done bypassing the firewall.

None
00:08:40,932 --> 00:08:42,934
And then, I just need to
decrypt the storage files.

None
00:08:44,269 --> 00:08:45,269
Wait...

None
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:47,440
Someone blocked my access!

None
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:48,399
Huh?

None
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:50,275
I can't get in! What the hell!

None
00:08:50,525 --> 00:08:52,443
- I need to re-route.
- I'm too dumb for this stuff.

None
00:08:52,445 --> 00:08:53,445
Hold on, hold on.

None
00:08:53,528 --> 00:08:54,529
Damn!

None
00:08:54,822 --> 00:08:55,822
What?!

None
00:08:56,115 --> 00:08:57,658
The system locked me out!

None
00:09:00,660 --> 00:09:01,828
Sorry, Keif.

None
00:09:02,620 --> 00:09:03,873
Can't get it this time around.

None
00:09:04,331 --> 00:09:06,875
I still can't get inside
the CCTV record archives.

None
00:09:07,168 --> 00:09:08,293
You did your best.

None
00:09:08,293 --> 00:09:10,211
Why don't we just get
a copy from the admin?

None
00:09:10,379 --> 00:09:11,297
That's right.

None
00:09:11,298 --> 00:09:12,629
Are you guys thinking straight?

None
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:13,756
We're Section E.

None
00:09:13,758 --> 00:09:15,759
Do you really think
that'll work? Good lord.

None
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:17,052
That makes sense.

None
00:09:18,596 --> 00:09:20,139
Well that's something else.

None
00:09:21,014 --> 00:09:22,639
You look genuinely
concerned for Jay-jay.

None
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,267
Hey!

None
00:09:23,268 --> 00:09:24,600
- Dumbass!
- Bad joke.

None
00:09:24,601 --> 00:09:26,269
Just kidding.
It was a joke, dude.

None
00:09:26,687 --> 00:09:28,063
Can't you take a joke?

None
00:09:29,606 --> 00:09:31,024
Oh? What now?

None
00:09:32,192 --> 00:09:33,192
Now...

None
00:09:33,568 --> 00:09:34,695
we move to Plan X.

None
00:09:35,071 --> 00:09:36,111
Let's go!

None
00:09:36,113 --> 00:09:37,739
That's in English, guys.
You got nothing on me.

None
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,740
This is fun.

None
00:09:39,658 --> 00:09:40,658
Hold on...

None
00:09:41,034 --> 00:09:42,284
Where is Yuri, by the way?

None
00:09:42,285 --> 00:09:43,995
- Why isn't he here?
- Yeah, you're right.

None
00:09:43,995 --> 00:09:44,996
Where is he?

None
00:09:45,163 --> 00:09:46,789
His hair is stark red and yet
you can't find him?

None
00:09:46,791 --> 00:09:47,956
He looks like a rooster
for god's sake!

None
00:09:47,957 --> 00:09:48,833
He's gone missing again.

None
00:09:48,835 --> 00:09:51,251
- Maybe he's in their shop.
- You asked about it, didn't you? Are you stupid?

None
00:09:51,253 --> 00:09:52,004
I'll beat your ass.

None
00:09:52,004 --> 00:09:53,004
Let's do one game?

None
00:09:53,005 --> 00:09:54,798
Huh? One more game?

None
00:09:55,048 --> 00:09:55,966
Let's go.

None
00:09:55,966 --> 00:09:57,726
- I don't really feel like it.
- Another one?

None
00:09:57,842 --> 00:09:59,259
All of you are soft.

None
00:09:59,260 --> 00:10:00,636
- Let me just get my things.
- Wow...

None
00:10:00,638 --> 00:10:01,596
Game, let's go!

None
00:10:01,597 --> 00:10:03,307
- But I was game.
- Did you hear that?

None
00:10:03,557 --> 00:10:04,640
- Soft.
- Let's play, guys.

None
00:10:04,642 --> 00:10:05,642
What does he mean?

None
00:10:07,186 --> 00:10:08,186
You asshole.

None
00:10:08,729 --> 00:10:11,774
When you said you're gonna take me home,
I thought you had a car.

None
00:10:14,735 --> 00:10:17,113
Hey! Don't hold me there!
I'm getting ticklish!

None
00:10:17,363 --> 00:10:20,782
- What's the problem?! The backseat is tiny!
- Just grab onto something else! Not there!

None
00:10:20,783 --> 00:10:21,700
Huh?!

None
00:10:21,701 --> 00:10:22,783
Here!

None
00:10:22,784 --> 00:10:25,035
Not there! On my shoulders!
Hold on to my shoulders!

None
00:10:25,037 --> 00:10:25,870
On your shoulders?

None
00:10:25,871 --> 00:10:27,998
- On my shoulders!
- [Jay-jay screams]

None
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,659
- Jay, are you okay?
- Ouch...

None
00:10:35,130 --> 00:10:36,548
Oh shit, you got hurt!

None
00:10:40,469 --> 00:10:41,469
Are you okay, Jay?

None
00:10:44,097 --> 00:10:45,432
Just a moment.
[Jay-jay flinches]

None
00:10:48,144 --> 00:10:49,726
- Slow down!
- You didn't listen to me!

None
00:10:49,727 --> 00:10:51,062
Be gentle with it!

None
00:10:52,022 --> 00:10:53,566
Come on, are you okay?

None
00:10:54,191 --> 00:10:56,277
- This is your fault.
- Hop in. Let's just go.

None
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,403
Let's just walk from here.

None
00:10:58,403 --> 00:10:59,404
No, ride the bike.

None
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:01,405
What if we fall again?!

None
00:11:01,407 --> 00:11:03,491
You're not gonna fall.
Just hop on.

None
00:11:05,827 --> 00:11:06,912
So pushy.

None
00:11:07,955 --> 00:11:09,581
You're so stubborn.
You can't stay still.

None
00:11:09,581 --> 00:11:11,249
- It's you who's stubborn.
- No, it's you.

None
00:11:11,250 --> 00:11:12,250
You are!

None
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,001
Am I the one driving?!

None
00:11:14,003 --> 00:11:15,171
Just get on it!

None
00:11:15,921 --> 00:11:17,465
My helmet!

None
00:11:21,384 --> 00:11:22,677
[Jay-jay groans]

None
00:11:22,677 --> 00:11:23,927
You're so slow. Just get on!

None
00:11:23,928 --> 00:11:25,014
Can't you wait?

None
00:11:26,097 --> 00:11:26,724
You good?

None
00:11:26,724 --> 00:11:27,724
Yeah.

None
00:11:28,057 --> 00:11:30,100
You're gonna walk?
Our house is still far from here.

None
00:11:30,101 --> 00:11:31,812
I can handle it, Jay. Just stay still.

None
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:33,980
Alright then.

None
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:34,980
Yeah.

None
00:11:38,110 --> 00:11:39,320
Are you okay, Jay?

None
00:11:39,653 --> 00:11:40,988
I should be asking you that.

None
00:11:41,614 --> 00:11:43,197
I told you I can walk.

None
00:11:43,198 --> 00:11:45,743
Just don't argue
anymore, Jay. Please.

None
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,538
Hey. It's here!

None
00:11:49,913 --> 00:11:50,413
Here?

None
00:11:50,414 --> 00:11:51,873
- Yeah. Here.
- Wait...

None
00:11:51,874 --> 00:11:52,917
Just stay still, alright?

None
00:11:56,253 --> 00:11:58,087
Hold on...

None
00:11:58,964 --> 00:12:00,130
What are you doing?

None
00:12:00,131 --> 00:12:02,384
Jay, don't be stubborn.
You can't even walk right now.

None
00:12:09,432 --> 00:12:10,475
Jay-jay!

None
00:12:11,143 --> 00:12:12,143
Jay...

None
00:12:13,937 --> 00:12:14,937
What's the matter?

None
00:12:15,688 --> 00:12:17,856
I'm sorry. I got her injured.

None
00:12:17,857 --> 00:12:19,150
Get down from there.

None
00:12:19,485 --> 00:12:21,195
It's embarrassing to your companion.

None
00:12:21,403 --> 00:12:23,197
But Grandma, he insists on carrying me.

None
00:12:24,740 --> 00:12:26,908
Grandma, do you have
a first-aid kit?

None
00:12:26,908 --> 00:12:29,202
Of course we do. Come on inside.

None
00:12:29,495 --> 00:12:30,913
Hurry up. Go on.

None
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,581
Your wound needs to be treated.

None
00:12:34,291 --> 00:12:35,208
Sorry...

None
00:12:35,208 --> 00:12:36,085
Quickly!

None
00:12:36,086 --> 00:12:37,253
You can put me down here.

None
00:12:37,418 --> 00:12:40,547
Come on. Here.
Over here.

None
00:12:41,465 --> 00:12:42,758
What on Earth happened to you?

None
00:12:43,759 --> 00:12:44,759
What happened?

None
00:12:46,386 --> 00:12:47,553
Put me down here.

None
00:12:48,054 --> 00:12:49,889
- Sorry, sorry.
- There, there, there.

None
00:12:50,265 --> 00:12:51,265
Thank you.

None
00:12:54,519 --> 00:12:55,894
- Here you go.
- Thank you.

None
00:12:55,895 --> 00:12:57,273
- I'll do it.
- Just let me, Jay.

None
00:13:09,909 --> 00:13:10,995
Where are you hurting?

None
00:13:19,211 --> 00:13:20,629
[Grandma reacts]

None
00:13:21,046 --> 00:13:23,881
He's gonna put an ointment.
That would sting.

None
00:13:26,677 --> 00:13:27,677
[Jay-jay flinches]

None
00:13:28,052 --> 00:13:29,846
Sorry, Jay. Sorry...

None
00:13:30,972 --> 00:13:32,265
Just a little more, Jay.

None
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,807
What happened?

None
00:13:33,808 --> 00:13:34,976
I have no idea.

None
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:38,937
Here it goes, Jay.

None
00:13:38,938 --> 00:13:40,023
I'll cover your wound.

None
