None
00:25:27,521 --> 00:25:29,355
[Section E teasing Jay-jay]

None
00:25:29,356 --> 00:25:31,482
- Don't be too stingy.
- Just one thank you.

None
00:25:31,483 --> 00:25:33,944
Wait! You're all so loud!
Why are you pressuring me?

None
00:25:34,194 --> 00:25:35,194
Keifer.

None
00:25:35,529 --> 00:25:36,529
Let me go first.

None
00:25:36,655 --> 00:25:37,655
[Ci-N clears throat]

None
00:25:38,950 --> 00:25:40,075
Thank you.

None
00:25:40,076 --> 00:25:41,702
[Section E boys laughing]

None
00:25:44,122 --> 00:25:45,372
So...

None
00:25:45,373 --> 00:25:46,373
your turn.

None
00:25:55,759 --> 00:25:58,094
You're so good! Alright!

None
00:25:59,429 --> 00:26:01,681
- Alright.
- You're okay now?

None
00:26:03,724 --> 00:26:07,700
What the fuck?!

None
00:26:09,001 --> 00:26:10,606
Freya! Language!

None
00:26:10,731 --> 00:26:11,816
Shut up!

None
00:26:15,778 --> 00:26:17,404
OMG.

None
00:26:17,696 --> 00:26:19,239
Is this your FaceGram account?

None
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:22,576
Well, duh? Are you dumb?
Hell yeah, it's mine.

None
00:26:22,951 --> 00:26:24,787
You can clearly see my name on it!

None
00:26:24,788 --> 00:26:27,663
There's my face on the DP.
It's so, so pretty.

None
00:26:27,664 --> 00:26:29,424
And then someone
will post trash like this?!

None
00:26:29,541 --> 00:26:32,211
My gosh. Who did this?!

None
00:26:32,836 --> 00:26:34,087
Maybe it was you!

None
00:26:34,088 --> 00:26:35,409
- Yeah.
- You're overacting

None
00:26:35,433 --> 00:26:37,811
I know you have my
password on your phone.

None
00:26:37,925 --> 00:26:39,176
I didn't touch your phone.

None
00:26:39,301 --> 00:26:42,387
I know you're obsessed with me since Day 1.
Just admit it, Kiko!

None
00:26:42,388 --> 00:26:43,855
You wish.

None
00:26:44,042 --> 00:26:46,433
You, come with me. Over here.

None
00:26:46,768 --> 00:26:47,768
Hey, you!

None
00:26:47,810 --> 00:26:48,185
Hey!

None
00:26:48,435 --> 00:26:51,355
Come! It was probably you, huh?!
What are you doing here?!

None
00:26:51,355 --> 00:26:53,607
We were instructed to do it.

None
00:26:54,318 --> 00:26:55,192
What's wrong, babe?

None
00:26:55,193 --> 00:26:56,861
That's why we did it.

None
00:27:00,949 --> 00:27:01,950
Open it.

None
00:27:02,282 --> 00:27:03,159
Show me your phone.

None
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,410
I wanna eat right now.
I'm so hungry!

None
00:27:05,411 --> 00:27:06,851
[Freya interrogating other students]

None
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:15,880
Just let them be, babe.

None
00:27:16,338 --> 00:27:18,298
It would be too obvious if we do something.

None
00:27:33,397 --> 00:27:34,648
What now?

None
00:27:35,191 --> 00:27:36,191
Pay what you owe.

None
00:27:37,777 --> 00:27:38,777
Huh?

None
00:27:39,863 --> 00:27:41,321
Oh, that.

None
00:27:42,323 --> 00:27:43,991
I still have nothing. Sorry.

None
00:27:45,326 --> 00:27:46,661
When are you going to pay me?

None
00:27:49,580 --> 00:27:50,580
I don't know.

None
00:27:50,748 --> 00:27:53,667
Didn't say thank you.
Didn't even pay.

None
00:27:54,251 --> 00:27:55,420
I get it.

None
00:27:56,753 --> 00:27:57,881
How about…

None
00:27:58,213 --> 00:28:00,090
you pay me with something else?

None
00:28:08,641 --> 00:28:09,641
You don't want to?

None
00:28:10,476 --> 00:28:11,476
Asshole!

None
00:28:12,436 --> 00:28:14,021
I'm just messing with you!

None
00:28:14,897 --> 00:28:15,897
Asshole.

None
00:28:19,402 --> 00:28:20,569
Just pay me with food.

None
00:28:20,903 --> 00:28:21,903
Food?

None
00:28:22,363 --> 00:28:24,240
I want one.
Bring food for me as well.

None
00:28:27,201 --> 00:28:28,202
Until when?

None
00:28:28,661 --> 00:28:29,953
Until graduation.

None
00:28:30,872 --> 00:28:31,914
Tough luck.

None
00:28:32,414 --> 00:28:35,000
You owe me twenty five thousand.
I'm practically getting nothing back.

None
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:36,626
Okay. It's 150 per lunch box.

None
00:28:36,627 --> 00:28:37,170
50.

None
00:28:37,170 --> 00:28:37,711
150.

None
00:28:37,711 --> 00:28:38,462
- 60.
- 150!

None
00:28:38,463 --> 00:28:40,214
You're overpricing!

None
00:28:40,298 --> 00:28:42,174
Prices of ingredients are extremely high!

None
00:28:45,260 --> 00:28:46,260
Hey!

None
00:28:46,804 --> 00:28:47,971
Let's just start today?

None
00:28:51,351 --> 00:28:52,351
So stubborn!

None
00:28:56,647 --> 00:28:58,398
Oh. I didn't know you were there.

None
00:28:58,982 --> 00:29:00,067
You told me, didn't you?

None
00:29:00,484 --> 00:29:01,484
Told you what?

None
00:29:01,861 --> 00:29:02,861
Lunch.

None
00:29:03,112 --> 00:29:05,990
Oh yeah!
Those two are waiting for us.

None
00:29:06,041 --> 00:29:07,041
Let's go.

None
00:29:09,493 --> 00:29:12,621
Finally, Jay, you're here.
We've been here forever.

None
00:29:12,622 --> 00:29:13,498
What took you so long?

None
00:29:13,499 --> 00:29:15,083
Look, my arms are getting skinnier...

None
00:29:15,415 --> 00:29:16,084
Oh?

None
00:29:16,291 --> 00:29:17,291
Hey.

None
00:29:17,460 --> 00:29:18,502
Why are you here, Yuri?

None
00:29:18,752 --> 00:29:20,128
He's gonna eat lunch with us.

None
00:29:21,338 --> 00:29:22,798
Grab a chair. Sit here.

None
00:29:24,133 --> 00:29:24,592
Ouch!

None
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:26,385
You guys really hang out here?

None
00:29:27,636 --> 00:29:28,805
Where is Calix, by the way?

None
00:29:29,012 --> 00:29:30,012
Calix?

None
00:29:30,138 --> 00:29:31,515
He's with Mica in the other room.

None
00:29:31,516 --> 00:29:32,516
Flirting.

None
00:29:32,849 --> 00:29:36,479
Let them be. They give me butterflies. They
only got back together recently, anyway.

None
00:29:37,105 --> 00:29:38,772
Oh. Here's your food.

None
00:29:40,316 --> 00:29:41,651
Cool!

None
00:29:41,984 --> 00:29:43,317
We're so famished!

None
00:29:43,318 --> 00:29:44,444
Thank you, Jay.

None
00:29:46,905 --> 00:29:48,199
We've been here for a long time.

None
00:29:49,701 --> 00:29:50,701
[Jay-jay sighs]

None
00:29:53,121 --> 00:29:54,538
[Ci-N and David happily chattering]

None
00:30:01,336 --> 00:30:02,336
What's this?

None
00:30:03,172 --> 00:30:04,172
Is this mine?

None
00:30:04,339 --> 00:30:05,674
I'm just asking you to open it.

None
00:30:07,384 --> 00:30:09,135
I'm joking. It's really yours.

None
00:30:09,136 --> 00:30:11,513
I felt sorry for you
when Keifer stole your food.

None
00:30:12,097 --> 00:30:14,142
Really? Is this for real?

None
00:30:25,111 --> 00:30:27,195
[Ci-N and David sighs in contentment]

None
00:30:28,655 --> 00:30:29,655
Say "ahh."

None
00:30:30,575 --> 00:30:31,575
"Ahh."

None
00:30:31,826 --> 00:30:32,826
"Ahh."

None
00:30:32,993 --> 00:30:34,369
- Bigger.
- Ah!

None
00:30:36,705 --> 00:30:37,705
[Yuri chuckles]

None
00:30:37,957 --> 00:30:39,076
What the hell. It's too big.

None
00:30:42,336 --> 00:30:43,336
It's so delicious!

None
00:30:43,337 --> 00:30:44,337
Here, eat up.

None
00:30:44,422 --> 00:30:45,422
It's good!

None
00:30:47,467 --> 00:30:48,633
Hey, you have your own food.

None
00:30:48,634 --> 00:30:49,760
Selfish.

None
00:30:50,053 --> 00:30:51,053
Just kidding.

None
00:30:51,471 --> 00:30:53,931
Good food can really make your day,
don't you think?

None
00:30:54,307 --> 00:30:55,516
Here, for the glutton.

None
00:30:56,183 --> 00:30:57,183
This is so delicious!

None
00:30:58,060 --> 00:30:59,354
This is my favorite!

None
00:31:00,063 --> 00:31:01,542
You know what,
I'll just use my hands.

None
00:31:03,273 --> 00:31:04,273
So yummy.

None
00:31:05,777 --> 00:31:07,693
Eating can really make
one happy, don't you think?

None
00:31:07,694 --> 00:31:10,490
But we would be so much happier
if we're eating at the canteen.

None
00:31:11,824 --> 00:31:12,991
If only we could.

None
00:31:13,409 --> 00:31:15,077
- Jay.
- Hmm?

None
00:31:17,413 --> 00:31:21,416
Whose side will you be on if ever…

None
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:22,911
Aries and Keifer fight again?

None
00:31:25,587 --> 00:31:27,339
I don't know. I'm torn.

None
00:31:29,967 --> 00:31:31,469
You don't need to choose.

None
00:31:32,303 --> 00:31:34,221
You've been caught in
our mess for far too long.

None
00:31:35,056 --> 00:31:38,518
No matter who you side with,
you'll still end up getting hurt.

None
00:31:39,769 --> 00:31:40,894
How can you say?

None
00:31:41,311 --> 00:31:44,022
You're part of Section E.
And Aries is your family.

None
00:31:44,565 --> 00:31:46,233
You think you won't get involved?

None
00:31:51,905 --> 00:31:52,905
Go on, eat up.

None
00:31:53,490 --> 00:31:54,075
Eat up.

None
00:31:54,450 --> 00:31:55,242
Do you want sushi?

None
00:31:55,326 --> 00:31:58,037
- You took my food. Give it back.
- Kidding, this is mine.

None
00:31:59,204 --> 00:32:00,330
Give it to me.

None
00:32:04,544 --> 00:32:06,921
Damn that asshole. He made my life harder.

None
00:32:07,422 --> 00:32:10,340
And of all times, my bike
broke down too. Such a hassle!

None
00:32:17,557 --> 00:32:18,557
Hi.

None
00:32:19,599 --> 00:32:20,599
It's you again?

None
00:32:22,060 --> 00:32:23,060
Going to school?

None
00:32:23,229 --> 00:32:23,813
Mm.

None
00:32:24,063 --> 00:32:25,605
You have a lot on your hands.

None
00:32:25,940 --> 00:32:27,460
I'm heading out.
I can give you a ride.

None
00:32:28,859 --> 00:32:29,943
No need. It's alright.

None
00:32:30,486 --> 00:32:32,613
Are you sure?
I'm heading the same way.

None
00:32:32,904 --> 00:32:34,155
You look like you're struggling.

None
00:32:34,156 --> 00:32:36,409
No, I'm alright. Go.

None
00:32:37,535 --> 00:32:38,535
Okay.

None
00:32:45,417 --> 00:32:46,417
That was weird.

None
00:32:56,261 --> 00:32:57,261
Are you deaf?

None
00:32:57,763 --> 00:32:58,972
I've been calling you.

None
00:32:59,682 --> 00:33:01,349
I thought it's for someone else.

None
00:33:02,727 --> 00:33:04,047
Get in. I'm taking you to school.

None
00:33:04,311 --> 00:33:05,686
Wow...

None
00:33:05,688 --> 00:33:08,064
Are you taking me to school because
you don't have a bike to steal?

None
00:33:08,065 --> 00:33:09,065
Get it.

None
00:33:09,525 --> 00:33:10,525
Okay.

None
00:33:10,609 --> 00:33:11,861
If you insist.

None
00:33:13,028 --> 00:33:14,028
So cool.

None
00:33:15,823 --> 00:33:16,949
[Jay-jay grunts in pain]

None
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,786
My body aches all over.

None
00:33:23,413 --> 00:33:25,165
You know, good thing
you gave me a ride.

None
00:33:27,064 --> 00:33:28,613
Why are you in our village again?

None
00:33:28,963 --> 00:33:32,173
Ah... I went somewhere nearby.

None
00:33:32,632 --> 00:33:33,798
At this early hour?

None
00:33:34,069 --> 00:33:35,069
Yeah.

None
00:33:35,734 --> 00:33:36,884
Lucky for me.

None
00:33:38,095 --> 00:33:40,013
What's in there? You look so worn out.

None
00:33:40,266 --> 00:33:43,308
These are lunch boxes I share with
David, Ci-N, and Keifer the asshole.

None
00:33:43,601 --> 00:33:45,353
Why are you packing
lunch for Keifer too?

None
00:33:45,685 --> 00:33:47,063
- Payment—
- Because she wants to.

None
00:33:47,688 --> 00:33:49,500
That's not true!
This is payment for my debt!

None
00:33:49,525 --> 00:33:50,525
Debt?

None
00:33:51,358 --> 00:33:52,359
I'll explain later.

None
00:33:54,862 --> 00:33:55,862
Hey!

None
00:33:56,530 --> 00:33:58,950
Give that back! I don't want to
hear an earful from you!

None
00:33:59,075 --> 00:34:00,075
Give it to me!

None
00:34:00,076 --> 00:34:01,284
I said, give it back!

None
00:34:01,285 --> 00:34:02,953
- Huh?
- Give it back now!

None
00:34:03,287 --> 00:34:04,287
Give it back!

None
00:34:04,913 --> 00:34:06,164
You're so annoying!

None
00:34:06,289 --> 00:34:09,000
Give it back, Keifer!
Stop treating me like a kid!

None
00:34:09,001 --> 00:34:10,293
My arms are getting tired.

None
00:34:10,628 --> 00:34:12,128
I'm getting tired!

None
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:14,880
There.

None
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:16,925
Look what you did.

None
00:34:17,802 --> 00:34:18,802
Give it to me.

None
00:34:20,637 --> 00:34:22,264
Give us some!

None
00:34:22,389 --> 00:34:24,307
- Hey! That's mine!
- Share this with us!

None
00:34:24,891 --> 00:34:26,686
- Give us some too!
- Take it here!

None
00:34:28,144 --> 00:34:29,313
[Section E boys clamoring]

None
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:33,442
It's all your fault!

None
00:34:36,403 --> 00:34:37,572
Class.

None
00:34:39,282 --> 00:34:40,574
Settle down.

None
00:34:41,617 --> 00:34:42,742
Go back to your seats.

None
00:34:43,536 --> 00:34:45,036
Let's talk about the festival.

None
00:34:47,248 --> 00:34:50,333
Aren't we far ahead of time?
Why are we discussing it this early?

None
00:34:50,668 --> 00:34:52,293
There is a chance that
it will be held earlier.

None
00:34:52,295 --> 00:34:54,422
So, it's better to discuss it
as early as possible.

None
00:34:55,797 --> 00:34:57,592
Yuri, what's with that festival?

None
00:34:59,135 --> 00:35:02,722
David. Will you please explain
to Jay-jay what the festival is?

None
00:35:02,929 --> 00:35:03,931
Yes, sir.

None
00:35:04,599 --> 00:35:07,559
So, the school festival.
It's a week-long celebration.

None
00:35:08,143 --> 00:35:12,648
There's a sports fest,
food stalls, booths, and a program.

None
00:35:13,356 --> 00:35:16,527
Whatever happens depends
on the rules of the school.

None
00:35:17,277 --> 00:35:18,195
There are rules?

None
00:35:18,195 --> 00:35:21,824
The number of booths depends
on the number of section representatives.

None
00:35:21,990 --> 00:35:24,534
As for the program, as usual,
it's going to be a pageant.

None
00:35:24,744 --> 00:35:26,077
Another pageant?

None
00:35:26,077 --> 00:35:27,829
Freya's gonna win again.

None
00:35:28,789 --> 00:35:32,043
When it comes to tasks,
A is in charge of the program.

None
00:35:32,251 --> 00:35:33,501
B for sports.

None
00:35:33,668 --> 00:35:34,710
C for booths.

None
00:35:34,711 --> 00:35:36,838
And D is tasked with security.

None
00:35:36,838 --> 00:35:38,382
And your section is night duty.

None
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:40,509
What do you mean by "night duty?"

None
00:35:40,842 --> 00:35:42,594
The festival runs for a whole week.

None
00:35:42,844 --> 00:35:44,722
Security is also needed at night.

None
00:35:45,056 --> 00:35:46,514
To watch the equipment.

None
00:35:47,182 --> 00:35:49,224
And to clean up all the garbage.

None
00:35:49,226 --> 00:35:51,101
- That's right!
- Yuck! It's disgusting!

None
00:35:51,103 --> 00:35:52,186
[Section E boys complaining]

None
00:35:52,188 --> 00:35:54,813
You're all good at complaining,
but you make me clean this place on my own!

None
00:35:54,815 --> 00:35:56,440
[Section E continues compaining]

None
00:35:56,442 --> 00:35:58,610
Class, class!

None
00:35:58,610 --> 00:36:01,280
They're gonna make us
clean the trash! Disgusting!

None
00:36:01,489 --> 00:36:03,490
Class! Class, class.

None
00:36:03,865 --> 00:36:05,157
You know the rules.

None
00:36:05,159 --> 00:36:08,202
You won't be allowed at the
festival if you don't do it.

None
00:36:08,204 --> 00:36:09,496
That's the old rule.

None
00:36:10,456 --> 00:36:12,916
I'm the class president now,
so it's going to change.

None
00:36:13,541 --> 00:36:15,335
Then what are you suggesting?

None
00:36:15,503 --> 00:36:16,878
We don't do any task.

None
00:36:17,253 --> 00:36:19,130
But then, you won't be
allowed to the festival.

None
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:21,882
That's too much.

None
00:36:21,884 --> 00:36:23,134
Mica and I are going on a date.

None
00:36:23,135 --> 00:36:24,677
I won't be able to watch Rakki's match.

None
00:36:24,679 --> 00:36:25,969
There's gonna be so much girls there.

None
00:36:25,971 --> 00:36:27,137
And food! Food!

None
00:36:27,139 --> 00:36:28,264
Here, eat this.

None
00:36:28,724 --> 00:36:31,016
I wanna go too!
I haven't been to the festival!

None
00:36:31,018 --> 00:36:32,018
No!

None
00:36:33,228 --> 00:36:34,688
My decision is final.

None
00:36:34,855 --> 00:36:37,108
No Festival. No tasks.

None
00:36:39,402 --> 00:36:40,860
You're only thinking about yourself!

None
00:36:41,112 --> 00:36:43,697
I'm just trying to save this
section from embarrassment.

None
00:36:44,197 --> 00:36:45,574
How about what we want?!

None
00:36:46,992 --> 00:36:48,034
What's it gonna be, boys?

None
00:36:48,284 --> 00:36:49,619
Wanna be humiliated?

None
00:36:49,786 --> 00:36:50,954
No...

None
00:36:50,954 --> 00:36:52,871
We don't want to clean garbage.

None
00:36:52,873 --> 00:36:54,081
- No, right?
- [Section E boys complaining]

None
00:36:54,083 --> 00:36:55,708
But! But! But!

None
00:36:55,710 --> 00:36:58,293
You want to go to the festival too, right?

None
00:36:58,295 --> 00:36:59,503
Of course!

None
00:36:59,505 --> 00:37:00,547
- See? See?
- [Section E boys agreeing]

None
00:37:00,547 --> 00:37:03,675
There! You, wanna go?
Two, three, four, five.

None
00:37:03,675 --> 00:37:04,510
Class...

None
00:37:04,510 --> 00:37:05,469
Then choose!

None
00:37:05,469 --> 00:37:06,804
Deal with the garbage...

None
00:37:07,221 --> 00:37:08,596
or hang out somewhere nice?

None
00:37:08,597 --> 00:37:09,597
Hang out!

None
00:37:11,684 --> 00:37:13,226
Wait, wait, wait.

None
00:37:13,226 --> 00:37:17,188
Or how about this...
enjoy the festival or just rot at home?

None
00:37:17,188 --> 00:37:19,565
- The Festival is more fun!
- Let's just hangout!

None
00:37:19,567 --> 00:37:21,650
[Section E arguing]

None
00:37:21,652 --> 00:37:23,360
Class! Class!

None
00:37:23,362 --> 00:37:25,405
[Section E arguing]

None
00:37:25,405 --> 00:37:27,326
- The festival's better, right?
- Enough, enough.

None
00:37:27,449 --> 00:37:28,284
Enough.

None
00:37:28,284 --> 00:37:31,327
The board hasn't finalized
the festival date yet.

None
00:37:31,327 --> 00:37:34,539
You still have time to decide
what you want to do.

None
00:37:36,125 --> 00:37:38,126
Now, let's just go back to our lesson.

None
00:37:40,083 --> 00:37:45,134
We'll be discussing the
literary structure particular

None
00:37:45,717 --> 00:37:47,177
[Jay-jay exhales]

None
00:37:50,389 --> 00:37:52,349
Here's my favorite subject.

None
00:37:53,016 --> 00:37:54,184
Lunch break.

None
00:37:54,184 --> 00:37:55,268
- Oh!
- There you go!

None
00:37:55,603 --> 00:37:56,603
Oh, Jay!

None
00:37:56,978 --> 00:37:59,023
It's just gonna be us
and David later, right?

None
00:37:59,856 --> 00:38:01,608
Maybe. Let's just be together.

None
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:03,860
Be together?

None
00:38:07,114 --> 00:38:07,864
Stop fooling around.

None
00:38:07,865 --> 00:38:09,300
- You're gonna get it from me.
- Tss.

None
00:38:09,324 --> 00:38:10,367
I'm just kidding.

None
00:38:11,619 --> 00:38:12,661
Why don't we eat?

None
00:38:13,286 --> 00:38:14,346
Let's go upstairs.

None
00:38:14,371 --> 00:38:15,731
Go ahead. I'll go after you, guys.

None
00:38:16,831 --> 00:38:17,831
Bring this with you.

None
00:38:19,835 --> 00:38:22,170
Yuri! I'll be there in a bit.
I'll just do something.

None
00:38:22,755 --> 00:38:23,755
Ah…

None
00:38:23,838 --> 00:38:25,887
- We can wait for you.
- Are you sure, Jay?

None
00:38:26,217 --> 00:38:26,884
Yeah, yeah.

None
00:38:26,884 --> 00:38:27,884
Alright.

None
00:38:27,949 --> 00:38:30,336
- Let's go, baby.
- I'm excited to eat.

None
00:38:35,266 --> 00:38:36,266
Here.

None
00:38:39,355 --> 00:38:40,355
Eat here.

None
00:38:42,483 --> 00:38:43,483
No way.

None
00:38:43,983 --> 00:38:45,443
Why do you have to eat there?

None
00:38:45,443 --> 00:38:46,320
Because we want to.

None
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:48,081
Are you really going to
dictate where we eat?

None
00:38:50,074 --> 00:38:51,074
Josh!

None
00:38:51,617 --> 00:38:52,742
Call Calix and the others.

None
00:38:54,161 --> 00:38:55,786
- Calix!
- Huh?

None
00:38:55,788 --> 00:38:59,235
- Keifer wants you back here.
- What now?

None
00:39:00,831 --> 00:39:02,333
Oh, what is it?

None
00:39:03,452 --> 00:39:05,065
I don't really know. He's mad.

None
00:39:05,188 --> 00:39:06,188
What the heck.

None
00:39:11,804 --> 00:39:13,097
Starting today...

None
00:39:13,597 --> 00:39:14,889
No one will eat upstairs.

None
00:39:16,307 --> 00:39:17,309
Everyone will stay here.

None
00:39:24,858 --> 00:39:26,818
Mica… Go on. Sit over there.

None
00:39:26,985 --> 00:39:27,985
Sit there, Calix.

None
00:39:31,782 --> 00:39:32,782
Food!

None
00:39:33,951 --> 00:39:34,951
And!

None
00:39:35,159 --> 00:39:36,579
No one will steal another's food.

None
00:39:37,079 --> 00:39:38,246
Bring your own food.

None
00:39:41,625 --> 00:39:42,625
Cool.

None
00:39:42,751 --> 00:39:43,126
Let's go.

None
00:39:43,543 --> 00:39:44,543
Yuri, let's sit together.

None
00:39:44,711 --> 00:39:45,711
Come on.

None
00:39:52,010 --> 00:39:53,010
Here's mine.

None
00:39:57,349 --> 00:39:57,932
Yuri.

None
00:39:58,182 --> 00:39:59,182
You're in my seat.

None
00:39:59,684 --> 00:40:00,101
Move.

None
00:40:00,393 --> 00:40:01,393
Move.

None
00:40:14,532 --> 00:40:15,532
Jay, what's your food?

None
00:40:16,784 --> 00:40:17,784
This…

None
00:40:18,621 --> 00:40:19,746
I brought your favorite.

None
00:40:20,204 --> 00:40:21,204
Wanna trade?

None
00:40:21,831 --> 00:40:22,831
Sure.

None
00:40:23,458 --> 00:40:24,458
Cool.

None
00:40:24,793 --> 00:40:26,295
- Thank you, Yuri.
- Thanks, too.

None
00:40:26,628 --> 00:40:27,628
Yes, let's eat!

None
00:40:28,172 --> 00:40:29,172
Thank you.

None
00:40:34,719 --> 00:40:36,400
- Can I have some?
- Hey, this is so tasty!

None
00:40:36,931 --> 00:40:37,931
Let me try some.

None
00:40:38,222 --> 00:40:40,768
Uhh, Jay… aren't we
gonna give them some?

None
00:40:41,518 --> 00:40:42,518
Yeah…

None
00:40:42,936 --> 00:40:44,146
Don't you feel sorry for us?

None
00:40:44,521 --> 00:40:46,231
We look like beggars here.

None
00:40:46,731 --> 00:40:48,650
Especially this one.
He also smells like one.

None
00:40:49,150 --> 00:40:49,652
Ouch.

None
00:40:50,027 --> 00:40:51,027
Boys,

None
00:40:51,195 --> 00:40:52,695
I apologize. The Old Man caught me.

None
00:40:53,237 --> 00:40:54,697
I can't bring food for you anymore.

None
00:40:57,076 --> 00:40:58,076
I have an idea!

None
00:40:58,242 --> 00:40:59,494
Why don't we cook for them?

None
00:40:59,744 --> 00:41:01,204
We have some
kitchenware here, right?

None
00:41:02,081 --> 00:41:03,081
Don't touch those.

None
00:41:03,831 --> 00:41:04,831
Once is enough.

None
00:41:05,668 --> 00:41:07,210
Here's your food. Let's eat this.

None
00:41:07,210 --> 00:41:07,920
Give me some!

None
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:09,356
We're not gonna touch those anymore.

None
00:41:09,380 --> 00:41:10,130
Those aren't ours.

None
00:41:10,130 --> 00:41:11,340
What if we break them?

None
00:41:12,925 --> 00:41:13,925
Who owns them?

None
00:41:15,302 --> 00:41:16,302
Superman.

None
00:41:16,719 --> 00:41:17,719
It's Eman.

None
00:41:17,887 --> 00:41:20,306
He's our classmate,
but he's been skipping school.

None
00:41:21,724 --> 00:41:23,284
Where is he? Why is he
skipping classes?

None
00:41:23,893 --> 00:41:24,936
He's at their restaurant.

None
00:41:25,311 --> 00:41:26,311
I heard…

None
00:41:26,438 --> 00:41:28,898
I heard that their business is failing,
so he has to work.

None
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:31,318
Why him? Where are his parents?

None
00:41:31,902 --> 00:41:32,902
God,

None
00:41:33,112 --> 00:41:34,911
his mother is a
good-for-nothing spendthrift.

None
00:41:34,947 --> 00:41:36,614
His father got into an accident.

None
00:41:36,990 --> 00:41:38,659
Burned his arm while cooking.

None
00:41:39,076 --> 00:41:40,119
That's unfortunate.

None
00:41:41,619 --> 00:41:42,619
Shall we visit him?

None
00:41:42,746 --> 00:41:43,496
Tss!

None
00:41:43,579 --> 00:41:44,579
You're meddling again.

None
00:41:45,164 --> 00:41:46,500
Sure. I'll come with you later.

None
00:41:46,791 --> 00:41:47,791
Me too.

None
00:41:47,835 --> 00:41:48,835
Okay, I'll go too.

None
00:41:49,420 --> 00:41:50,461
Let's go as well, baby.

None
00:41:50,628 --> 00:41:51,628
Mmhm.

None
00:42:05,853 --> 00:42:06,853
Are we here?

None
00:42:09,148 --> 00:42:10,648
Does Eman's family really own this?

None
00:42:11,025 --> 00:42:12,108
So cool.

None
00:42:12,443 --> 00:42:14,695
Have you been here?
Looks like their food's delicious.

None
00:42:16,322 --> 00:42:17,655
I wonder what their specialty is.

None
00:42:21,784 --> 00:42:24,038
See? You can't say no to us.

None
00:42:25,039 --> 00:42:27,056
- Five more minutes, sir.
- Are you serious?

None
00:42:27,081 --> 00:42:29,043
I'm really sorry. Wait just a moment.

None
00:42:30,460 --> 00:42:31,460
Welcome.

None
00:42:32,045 --> 00:42:33,775
Good morning. Are you open?

None
00:42:34,172 --> 00:42:35,940
Yes. Table for how many?

None
00:42:35,965 --> 00:42:36,965
He's asking us.

None
00:42:37,842 --> 00:42:39,422
We're not here to eat. Remember?

None
00:42:40,971 --> 00:42:41,972
Is Eman here?

None
00:42:42,472 --> 00:42:44,472
He's in the kitchen.
Do you need anything from him?

None
00:42:44,682 --> 00:42:46,476
Tell him Section E is here.

None
00:42:46,726 --> 00:42:48,853
Tell him to come out
and don't keep us waiting.

None
00:42:49,146 --> 00:42:50,146
Please.

None
00:42:54,485 --> 00:42:55,485
I'll handle this.

None
00:42:55,693 --> 00:42:56,693
Alright.

None
00:42:57,945 --> 00:42:58,945
What do you need?

None
00:42:59,280 --> 00:43:00,601
We want to know how you're doing.

None
00:43:00,690 --> 00:43:02,108
Then you can feed us after.

None
00:43:03,190 --> 00:43:04,552
Is that really why you're here?

None
00:43:04,661 --> 00:43:08,121
No. I want to ask permission
to use your things back at school.

None
00:43:08,123 --> 00:43:09,568
Maybe we can borrow them.

None
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:11,000
Use them.

None
00:43:11,126 --> 00:43:12,126
Do what you want.

None
00:43:12,594 --> 00:43:14,938
I'm gonna quit school
so… you can have those.

None
00:43:15,713 --> 00:43:16,713
Is that true?

None
00:43:17,007 --> 00:43:18,311
You're really gonna quit?

None
00:43:18,717 --> 00:43:20,039
You see my situation here.

None
00:43:20,719 --> 00:43:22,599
I'm needed at the restaurant.

None
00:43:23,347 --> 00:43:24,869
Only three of us are left here.

None
00:43:25,226 --> 00:43:26,855
Are you managing the restaurant?

None
00:43:28,434 --> 00:43:30,105
Your dad was the chef here, right?

None
00:43:30,728 --> 00:43:31,728
Who's cooking?

None
00:43:32,063 --> 00:43:32,826
Now?

None
00:43:33,023 --> 00:43:33,706
It's me.

None
00:43:33,940 --> 00:43:34,940
What's taking so long?!

None
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:36,400
I apologize, sir.

None
00:43:37,027 --> 00:43:39,106
I have to go back to the
kitchen. We have customers.

None
00:43:39,362 --> 00:43:40,362
Hey, Eman!

None
00:43:41,782 --> 00:43:43,157
We're not done talking to you.

None
00:43:44,034 --> 00:43:45,034
Please.

None
00:43:45,327 --> 00:43:46,327
I have work to do.

None
00:43:46,661 --> 00:43:47,661
So, what's your plan?

None
00:43:48,454 --> 00:43:49,454
Right now?

None
00:43:49,581 --> 00:43:50,581
Go back to work.

None
00:43:53,126 --> 00:43:57,547
Ma'am, sir. Please take a seat and wait.
We apologize.

None
00:44:01,300 --> 00:44:02,302
What are you doing?

None
00:44:03,719 --> 00:44:04,719
Here's our menu.

None
00:44:05,097 --> 00:44:06,097
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

None
00:44:06,889 --> 00:44:07,889
We're gonna help here.

None
00:44:07,932 --> 00:44:08,932
What?

None
00:44:10,811 --> 00:44:13,289
We're gonna help until
your restaurant recovers.

None
00:44:13,355 --> 00:44:14,521
Until you're able to hire more crew.

None
00:44:14,523 --> 00:44:16,190
And who's "we"?

None
00:44:17,483 --> 00:44:18,483
Calix and I will help.

None
00:44:19,510 --> 00:44:21,454
And me. I'll help out too.

None
00:44:21,822 --> 00:44:22,822
Alright, me too.

None
00:44:23,532 --> 00:44:25,242
We can do shifting amongst ourselves.

None
00:44:26,284 --> 00:44:27,786
Yeah, and then just pay us with food.

None
00:44:29,538 --> 00:44:31,581
It's obvious I can't stop you.

None
00:44:33,500 --> 00:44:35,168
Brother… please guide them.

None
00:44:35,793 --> 00:44:37,673
Make sure they're not
gonna cause any problems.

None
00:44:38,880 --> 00:44:40,465
Bro, I'll handle that.

None
00:44:42,675 --> 00:44:43,177
Tss.

None
00:44:43,427 --> 00:44:45,429
Miss Meddler strikes again.

None
00:44:45,721 --> 00:44:47,264
Ma'am, sir. Here's your order.

None
00:44:49,016 --> 00:44:50,016
Oh, thank you.

None
00:44:50,057 --> 00:44:51,101
Are you ready to order?

None
00:44:51,434 --> 00:44:52,684
Baby, there's a customer.

None
00:44:52,686 --> 00:44:54,353
We have all meat pizza…

None
00:44:54,353 --> 00:44:55,646
standard pizza...

None
00:44:57,148 --> 00:44:58,192
Do you have extra aprons?

None
00:44:58,496 --> 00:44:59,842
Ma'am, What's your order?

None
00:45:00,360 --> 00:45:01,445
Do you want to try this?

None
00:45:01,485 --> 00:45:02,485
Calix.

None
00:45:03,322 --> 00:45:05,615
You're gonna try everything?
Here's our bestseller.

None
00:45:05,639 --> 00:45:06,592
That soup.

None
00:45:06,617 --> 00:45:10,036
For drinks, we have juices,
hot drinks, soft drinks…

None
00:45:11,277 --> 00:45:11,954
Everything.

None
00:45:12,206 --> 00:45:13,206
Everything?

None
00:45:13,789 --> 00:45:15,375
I'll tell the rest of the class myself.

None
00:45:16,918 --> 00:45:18,855
- Oh, alright.
- Have you dined here before, Miss?

None
00:45:18,878 --> 00:45:19,878
You know our menu!

None
00:45:26,637 --> 00:45:28,304
- Here's your order, Sir.
- Thank you.

None
00:45:28,304 --> 00:45:29,264
Enjoy your meal.

None
00:45:29,264 --> 00:45:30,264
Thank you.

None
00:45:33,184 --> 00:45:34,436
Come here.

None
00:45:37,231 --> 00:45:38,231
Smile.

None
00:45:38,398 --> 00:45:38,940
What?

None
00:45:39,023 --> 00:45:40,023
Smile.

None
00:45:42,902 --> 00:45:43,902
Like this.

None
00:45:44,528 --> 00:45:45,528
There!

None
00:45:46,447 --> 00:45:47,615
He's so handsome.

None
00:45:48,157 --> 00:45:48,659
Go on.

None
00:45:49,159 --> 00:45:50,159
Smile, okay?

None
00:45:52,329 --> 00:45:53,472
He's coming, he's coming.

None
00:45:53,496 --> 00:45:54,896
Your orders are coming up.

None
00:45:55,123 --> 00:45:56,123
Okay.

None
00:45:56,333 --> 00:45:59,043
[customers screaming]

None
00:45:59,585 --> 00:46:00,836
Heres' your change.

None
00:46:00,862 --> 00:46:02,222
Do you have any additional orders?

None
00:46:03,172 --> 00:46:05,300
Thank you! Did you like the food?

None
00:46:06,385 --> 00:46:07,842
It was delicious.
We're gonna come back.

None
00:46:07,844 --> 00:46:08,844
Thank you.

None
00:46:09,096 --> 00:46:10,806
Your service was exemplary.

None
00:46:10,889 --> 00:46:12,474
Thank you very much.

None
00:46:12,516 --> 00:46:13,641
5 star!

None
00:46:13,891 --> 00:46:14,891
Wow.

None
00:46:15,226 --> 00:46:16,489
Thank you!

None
00:46:16,519 --> 00:46:18,105
Oh, please come see us again.

None
00:46:18,275 --> 00:46:21,402
Take care. Please do come back.

None
00:46:26,195 --> 00:46:27,195
Oh.

None
00:46:27,655 --> 00:46:28,775
I thought you're gonna help?

None
00:46:29,949 --> 00:46:30,949
Did I say that?

None
00:46:33,661 --> 00:46:34,661
Oh gosh,

None
00:46:35,579 --> 00:46:36,873
you're miles behind Yuri.

None
00:46:36,998 --> 00:46:37,998
Look.

None
00:46:38,958 --> 00:46:39,958
Baby!

None
00:46:40,876 --> 00:46:41,876
Thank you.

None
00:46:42,211 --> 00:46:43,211
My baby is so cute.

None
00:46:43,213 --> 00:46:44,922
- You're from HVIS, right? Grade 12?
- Yeah.

None
00:46:44,922 --> 00:46:47,550
I saw you at school.
Red hair. It's really you!

None
00:46:48,342 --> 00:46:49,342
Look at Yuri.

None
00:46:49,885 --> 00:46:51,054
Do what he's doing.

None
00:46:53,681 --> 00:46:54,365
Just stay here, okay?

None
00:46:54,391 --> 00:46:56,684
Okay, we're really not going anywhere.

None
00:47:08,612 --> 00:47:09,612
Hey,

None
00:47:09,822 --> 00:47:11,114
our shift's not over yet.

None
00:47:11,115 --> 00:47:12,315
The others are still coming...

None
00:47:14,286 --> 00:47:15,286
Ah.

None
00:47:31,260 --> 00:47:33,137
[customers screaming]

None
00:47:36,516 --> 00:47:37,934
Look over there.

None
00:47:38,809 --> 00:47:40,186
What happened to him?

None
00:47:41,788 --> 00:47:43,123
Are you ready to order?

None
00:47:43,148 --> 00:47:44,856
The winds have
changed direction, huh?

None
00:47:47,402 --> 00:47:49,445
[customers screaming]

None
00:47:49,653 --> 00:47:50,813
But it's effective, isn't it?

None
00:47:54,701 --> 00:47:56,661
So… can you just repeat your order?

None
00:47:57,079 --> 00:47:58,704
Hey! What are you doing?

None
00:47:59,081 --> 00:48:00,289
It's scorching hot in here.

None
00:48:02,083 --> 00:48:03,083
What's your order?

None
00:48:03,418 --> 00:48:04,418
That's okay.

None
00:48:04,585 --> 00:48:06,420
Just seeing you is enough for us.

None
00:48:08,255 --> 00:48:09,255
Here's your order.

None
00:48:09,257 --> 00:48:11,675
[screaming continues]

None
00:48:15,054 --> 00:48:16,614
Of course, I'm gonna come back for you.

None
00:48:17,932 --> 00:48:19,652
Are you sure that's all you're gonna order?

None
00:48:20,936 --> 00:48:21,936
Sis?

None
00:48:24,313 --> 00:48:26,751
- You? Can we order you?
- Picture? How about a picture? A selfie.

None
00:48:26,775 --> 00:48:27,775
- Selfie?
- Sure.

None
00:48:31,487 --> 00:48:32,197
Go on, eat.

None
00:48:32,405 --> 00:48:34,240
To check your order…

None
00:48:34,407 --> 00:48:36,742
one order of everything in the menu.

None
00:48:36,742 --> 00:48:38,994
Can I touch your biceps?

None
00:48:42,039 --> 00:48:44,708
You wanna feel it?

None
00:48:53,427 --> 00:48:54,302
Can we touch it again?

None
00:48:54,344 --> 00:48:55,344
Go on.

None
00:49:12,487 --> 00:49:13,487
What's up, boys?

None
00:49:13,989 --> 00:49:14,989
Yo!

None
00:49:16,699 --> 00:49:19,661
[Section E boys greeting each other]

None
00:49:29,588 --> 00:49:31,338
Because of my meddling,

None
00:49:33,257 --> 00:49:38,054
we were able to help Eman and his family.

None
00:49:44,728 --> 00:49:47,938
I hope they all stay like this.

None
00:49:56,155 --> 00:49:57,282
Oh! Hey!

None
00:49:58,617 --> 00:49:59,617
Ouch!

None
00:49:59,742 --> 00:50:01,327
Ci! Ci! Wipe the floor, please.

None
00:50:02,177 --> 00:50:02,929
What happened?

None
00:50:03,007 --> 00:50:03,800
Go sit over here.

None
00:50:03,954 --> 00:50:04,954
Just sit down.

None
00:50:05,123 --> 00:50:06,670
Put it down. Sit over here.

None
00:50:07,416 --> 00:50:08,416
Go on, sit.

None
00:50:08,751 --> 00:50:10,503
Eman, do you have a first aid kit?

None
00:50:16,443 --> 00:50:17,771
Thank you.

None
00:50:18,425 --> 00:50:19,425
Let me see it.

None
00:50:27,228 --> 00:50:28,228
Sorry, sorry, sorry.

None
00:50:31,942 --> 00:50:33,527
You know this is your fault, right?

None
00:50:34,777 --> 00:50:35,778
Okay, already.

None
00:50:36,070 --> 00:50:37,905
I'm treating your wound now, right?

None
00:50:38,657 --> 00:50:40,157
Why do you have to meddle in things?

None
00:50:40,951 --> 00:50:42,271
Why don't you just let things be?

None
00:50:43,744 --> 00:50:44,744
Give it to me.

None
00:51:07,601 --> 00:51:08,644
What's the reason?

None
00:51:10,313 --> 00:51:11,313
Huh?

None
00:51:13,400 --> 00:51:15,360
Why can't stay away from
other people's problems?

None
00:51:18,862 --> 00:51:19,862
Sorry, sorry.

None
00:51:23,827 --> 00:51:25,077
I just can't help it.

None
00:51:29,708 --> 00:51:30,916
I can't just do nothing...

None
00:51:32,626 --> 00:51:34,420
when I know things can change.

None
00:51:36,523 --> 00:51:37,798
But nobody even tries.

None
00:51:38,257 --> 00:51:39,425
Nobody believes.

None
00:51:41,844 --> 00:51:44,085
If things can get better, why
not do something about it?

None
00:51:47,559 --> 00:51:49,101
You know you can't change everyone.

None
00:51:49,936 --> 00:51:50,936
It's okay.

None
00:51:52,188 --> 00:51:53,188
At least I tried.

None
00:51:56,693 --> 00:51:57,693
Hmm.

None
00:51:58,320 --> 00:51:59,487
We're even now.

None
00:52:16,690 --> 00:52:17,690
Thank you.

None
00:53:56,228 --> 00:53:57,771
OMG.

None
00:53:58,523 --> 00:54:01,233
So it's true. You're also
a waitress now.

None
00:54:01,233 --> 00:54:03,074
Keifer Watson. Is your family
getting poor now?

None
00:54:03,235 --> 00:54:04,777
How did Aries know we're here?

None
00:54:04,778 --> 00:54:06,070
Will they cause a scene here?

None
00:54:06,072 --> 00:54:07,574
Why would Kiko suddenly court you?!

None
00:54:07,824 --> 00:54:08,949
And you're letting him?!

None
00:54:08,949 --> 00:54:09,742
The thing is…

None
00:54:09,742 --> 00:54:10,367
You like him.

None
00:54:10,702 --> 00:54:12,996
No. I'm not letting
him court me.

None
00:54:13,121 --> 00:54:15,414
You were smitten by his
American accent and sweet smiles.

None
00:54:15,414 --> 00:54:16,039
That's not true.

None
00:54:16,041 --> 00:54:17,331
You don't like English-speaking guys?

None
00:54:17,333 --> 00:54:18,001
No.

None
00:54:18,001 --> 00:54:19,001
How about Keifer?

None
00:54:19,293 --> 00:54:20,128
[Ci-N teasing Jay-jay]

None
00:54:20,128 --> 00:54:21,128
Will you stop that?!

None
00:54:21,295 --> 00:54:22,376
Do you really like Jay-jay?

None
00:54:22,755 --> 00:54:24,672
Jay-jay is not allowed
to have a boyfriend.

None
00:54:24,673 --> 00:54:25,798
What is wrong with you?

None
00:54:25,800 --> 00:54:26,634
You know me.

None
00:54:26,634 --> 00:54:27,342
Exactly.

None
00:54:27,344 --> 00:54:28,385
- Hey!
- [ Jay-jay gets startled]

None
00:54:28,385 --> 00:54:29,137
What are you doing here?

None
00:54:29,304 --> 00:54:29,846
Get in.

None
00:54:30,262 --> 00:54:31,304
Why do you need to fetch me?

None
00:54:31,306 --> 00:54:32,347
You want some?

None
00:54:33,141 --> 00:54:34,141
I know you do.

None
00:54:39,063 --> 00:54:40,543
There's something
different about you.

None
00:54:41,023 --> 00:54:42,025
Are you wearing contacts?

None
00:54:43,693 --> 00:54:45,277
Oh no… what happened to you?

None
00:54:45,277 --> 00:54:46,128
Fuck them!

None
00:54:46,153 --> 00:54:48,130
We should retaliate.
Who's with me?

None
00:54:48,155 --> 00:54:49,739
You can't come, Jay.

None
00:54:49,740 --> 00:54:50,909
And why not?

None
00:54:50,992 --> 00:54:52,492
Because you're gonna
fight again, don't you?

None
00:54:52,494 --> 00:54:54,579
You're putting yourselves
in danger because of me.

